# 📦 System Dependencies & Libraries

This document outlines all required libraries and dependencies for the 3-tier Dual Reciprocating Drill architecture. It is separated by hardware tier to make environment setup as easy as possible.

---

## 💻 Tier 1: Windows Command Center (HMI)
**Environment:** Python 3.9+

This tier runs the graphical user interface and parses the incoming OpenCV video stream and JSON telemetry.

### External Packages
Open your Windows Command Prompt or PowerShell and install the following:
```bash
pip install PyQt6 opencv-python
